New Records: Oklahoma City Thunder achieved a franchise-record 15th straight win.
Key Match Events: Shai Gilgeous-Alexander scored 33 points and grabbed 11 rebounds.
Jayson Tatum led the Celtics with 26 points and 10 rebounds.
Oklahoma City Thunder pulled away in the fourth quarter with a 29-12 run.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The game was held at Paycom Center in Oklahoma City with an attendance of 18,203.
Referees for the game were Tom Washington, Scott Foster, and Mousa Dagher.
